Title: Murphy Brown Lied to Us
Plot: Jack sets Liz up on a blind date to show her what she's missing in her relationship with Criss. Meanwhile at KableTown, Jack has to scramble when his plan to manufacture couches hits a speed bump. With Tracy's help, Jenna orchestrates a public meltdown to get Paul's attention.
GuestStars: James Marsden, Stacy Keach, Will Forte, Bobby Moynihan, Matt Lauer, Vinny Anand, Tom McNutt, Bebe Wood, Curt Bouril, Stephen Beach, Paul Juhn, Steven Hauck, Kelly Deadmon, Dhruvi Patel
